Male terminalia (Fig. 17
A-D
): epandrium with ca. 16 setae near posterior and ventral margins per side. Surstylus with five peg-like prensisetae. Hypandrium with a pair of paramedian setae, lacking pubescence. Paramere with five sensilla and pubescence medially. Aedeagus with pubescence ventrally.
